{"about_the_game":"Board the Brix Core, piloted by Prince Brix himself. Combine aircrafts in different ways to gain abilities and grab crystals to boost your firepower. <br>It'll take split-second decisions, expert control, and a bit of luck to survive this gauntlet. Can Prince Brix defeat the evil looming before him and save the world? <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1115580/extras/Ray_GIF-min.gif?t=1693958016\" /><br><br>Game Features<br>- Fusion system lets you combine with randomly-appearing aircrafts<br>- Upgrade system lets you collect experience points to power up your aircraft<br>- Strategic elements - change crafts at the right time to survive the waves of bullets<br>- Secret units with massive power<br>- Challenge Mode lets you compete with friends for high scores<br>- Online leaderboard encourages you to step up your game<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1115580/extras/Fusion_GIF-min.gif?t=1693958016\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Basic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1115580/5817dcbe9a7a599ce0bd4dc9aee8e90ed74eb3c4.jpg"},{"name":"Impressive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1115580/c5db32631d360ccafd197d5792d39220bf17d4b8.jpg"},{"name":"Nothing's Impossible","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1115580/2fea915782a2b2feeddf143fb8f5c8437a110dbc.jpg"},{"name":"New is Good","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1115580/674ad889ad4a06d7f822cbe4cc8b65b724a96c3e.jpg"},{"name":"I won't miss Anything","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1115580/2959aa437c66fbb12f7376b571676cca0505ce80.jpg"},{"name":"Well begun is Half-done","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1